lead_paragraph: Anthony Davis hit a pair of free throws with 12 seconds left and scored 32 points, and the New Orleans Pelicans got their first victory after losing their first eight by beating the Milwaukee Bucks 112-106 on Thursday night.

headline.print_headline: Davis Scores 32, Pelicans Beat Bucks 112-106 for First Win
